             was indicted for <rs id="t18301028-71-off391" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301028-71-off391" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301028-71-off391" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301028-71-cd392" type="crimeDate">17th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-71-off391 t18301028-71-cd392"></join>, 10 saws, value 2s. 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18301028-71-victim651" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Hawkins
                        <interp inst="t18301028-71-victim651" type="surname" value="Hawkins"></interp>
